    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Script associated with Western Europen manuscripts of the 12th century. It is a transitional script between late Carolingian and Gothic textura that assumes an oval aspect and some lateral compression of minims.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
